#: ../../source/soft_connection.rst:2
msgid "Soft Connection"
msgstr "软连接"

#: ../../source/soft_connection.rst:4
msgid ""
"Soft connection is a spring, which constraint two rigidbody. But soft "
"connection only constraint location. Often used for lateral constraints "
"on skirts or cloaks to prevent excessive mesh deformation. If you wan to "
"make the floating widget, set the joint instead, because soft connection "
"can not constraint angle."
msgstr ""
"软连接是一个弹簧，约束两个刚体。 但软连接仅约束位置。 通常用于裙子或斗篷上的横向约束，以防止网格过度变形。 "
"如果你想制作浮动部件，请设置关节，因为软连接不能约束角度。"

#: ../../source/soft_connection.rst:6
msgid ""
"In rigidbody modify mode, you can press Ctrl+W to add soft connection in "
"batch(skirt using \"tube\" option, cope using \"plane\" option, create "
"single soft connection using \"pair\" option)"
msgstr "在刚体修改模式下，可以按Ctrl+W批量添加软连接（裙边使用“tube”选项，coe使用“plane”选项，创建单个软连接使用“pair”选项）"

#: ../../source/soft_connection.rst:18
msgid "In Rigidbody Modify Mode"
msgstr "在刚体修改模式下"

#: ../../source/soft_connection.rst:19
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Ctrl+W, create soft connection. \"Pair\", set soft connection to two "
"selected two rigidbody bone. \"Tube\" and \"plane\", set soft connection "
"for multiple bone chain (multiple bone chains should have the same number"
" of bones), \"Tube\" for skirt, \"Plane\" for cloak or hair."
msgstr ""
"Ctrl+W，创建软连接。 “成对”，设置软连接到两个选定的两个刚体骨骼。 "
"“管状”和“面状”，为多个骨链设置软连接（多个骨链应该是相同数量的骨头），“管”用于裙子，“平面”用于斗篷或头发。"

#: ../../source/soft_connection.rst:21
msgid "Shift+W, set selected rigidobdy bone soft connection property."
msgstr "Shift+W，设置选中的刚体骨骼软连接属性。"

#: ../../source/soft_connection.rst:23
msgid "Alt+W, delete selected rigidobdy bone soft connection."
msgstr "Alt+W，删除选定的刚体骨骼软连接。"

